outputs.output_descr: By 2013, national capacities enhanced for strengthening self-help groups to undertake agro-based rural livelihoods, community-driven, productivity-enhancing small rural works with special focus on women including those living with HIV/AIDS and for improved implementation of conditional cash transfers to vulnerable women
Improved access of the Tono market community to clean water and sanitation, and improved security and safety in the market through provision of well-lit and safe market conditions.

project_descr: Reduction of poverty in Oecusse district through Self Help Groups and improved agro-technologies and cattle raising techniques.
